OL,3,C'Alarming' drop in UK consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence over last year ` Which?
OL,6,FConsumer confidence in the future UK
OL,7,Feconomy has plummeted over the last
OL,8,Fyear, figures suggest.
OL,10,FConfidence has tumbled by 31 points
OL,11,Fover the last year, from an average of
OL,12,Fminus nine between May and July 2024
OL,13,Fto an average of minus 40 between May
OL,14,Fand July this year, Which?'s Consumer
OL,15,FInsight Tracker shows.
OL,17,FOn average between this May and July,
OL,18,F56% of people thought the economy
OL,19,Fwould get worse and just 16% thought
OL,20,Fit would get better.
