OL,3,C'Alarming' drop in UK consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence over last year ` Which?
OL,6,FWhich? said the figures showed a
OL,7,F"significant fall" to some of the
OL,8,Flowest levels seen since early 2023,
OL,9,Fwhen the cost-of-living crisis was in
OL,10,Fthe headlines and inflation was in
OL,11,Fdouble figures.
OL,13,FConfidence in the future economy
OL,14,Fdeclined sharply last autumn and was
OL,15,Fparticularly low between February to
OL,16,FMay, when global events such as the US
OL,17,Ftariff policy contributed to the
OL,18,Fpessimism.
