OL,3,C'Alarming' drop in UK consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence over last year ` Which?
OL,6,FConfidence had recovered a little
OL,7,Fsince, but remained considerably lower
OL,8,Fthan 12 months ago.
OL,10,FPensioners have been the most
OL,11,Fpessimistic group, with their
OL,12,Fconfidence in the future UK economy
OL,13,Ffalling dramatically from an average
OL,14,Fof minus five between May and July
OL,15,Flast year to a current average of
OL,16,Fminus 63.
