OL,3,C'Alarming' drop in UK consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence over last year ` Which?
OL,6,FPensioners' confidence dropped
OL,7,Fdramatically in autumn last year `
OL,8,Fshortly after the Government's first
OL,9,Fannouncement of scrapping the winter
OL,10,Ffuel allowance for most pensioners `
OL,11,Fand has remained low since, in spite
OL,12,Fof the Government U-turn on fuel
OL,13,Fpayments.
OL,15,FWhich?'s figures suggest that
OL,16,Ffinancial difficulties from the height
OL,17,Fof the cost-of-living crisis are yet
OL,18,Fto return to the pre-crisis levels.
