OL,3,C'Alarming' drop in UK consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence over last year ` Which?
OL,6,FIn the month to July 18, an estimated
OL,7,F2.1 million households missed at least
OL,8,Fone essential payment such as rent or
OL,9,Fmortgage payments, utility bills,
OL,10,Fcredit card or loan payments.
OL,12,FAn estimated 13.9 million households
OL,13,F(49%) also made at least one
OL,14,Fadjustment to cover essential spending
OL,15,Fsuch as utility bills, housing costs,
OL,16,Fgroceries, school supplies and
OL,17,Fmedicines in the last month ` such as
OL,18,Fcutting back on essentials, dipping
OL,19,Finto savings, selling possessions or
OL,20,Fborrowing.
