OL,3,C'Alarming' drop in UK consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence over last year ` Which?
OL,6,FRocio Concha, Which? director of
OL,7,Fpolicy and advocacy, said: "Our
OL,8,Fresearch shows consumer confidence in
OL,9,Fthe future of the UK economy has
OL,10,Fdropped alarmingly over the last year.
OL,12,F"The Government has rightly focused on
OL,13,Fgrowing the economy and raising living
OL,14,Fstandards but in doing so, it must not
OL,15,Foverlook the importance of consumer
OL,16,Fprotections in restoring confidence.
