OL,3,C'Alarming' drop in UK consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence over last year ` Which?
OL,6,F"People are sick to the teeth of
OL,7,Fhaving to dodge fraudsters when
OL,8,Fshopping online, watching out for
OL,9,Frogue traders when making home
OL,10,Fimprovements and needing to keep an
OL,11,Feye out for dodgy pricing practices
OL,12,Fwhich mean that offers aren't as good
OL,13,Fas they first appear.
OL,15,F"The right consumer protections give
OL,16,Fpeople the confidence to spend and the
OL,17,FGovernment must place these
OL,18,Fprotections at the heart of its plans
OL,19,Fto grow the economy."
